</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 61.2px;">
<td style="width: 17.6038%; border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000;">
<p><span data-path-to-node="4,3,0,0"><strong>Classes:</strong></span></p>
</td>
<td style="width: 77.127%; border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000;">
<p><span data-path-to-node="4,3,1,0">First group – Mrs. Oliver</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 61.2px;">
<td style="width: 17.6038%; border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000;"> </td>
<td style="width: 77.127%; border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000;">
<p><span data-path-to-node="4,4,1,0">Second group – Mrs. {Keogh}</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
