<p><span data-path-to-node="4,5,0,0"><strong>Hours &amp; Days:</strong></span></p>
</td>
<td style="width: 77.127%; border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000;">
<p><span data-path-to-node="4,5,1,0">Suzie will attend 3 days a week for a total of {15} hours</span></p>
